library(httr)
library(maptools)
library(maps)
library(mapdata)
library(rjson)
library(stringr)
library(RCurl)
library(ggplot2)
library(plyr)
library(ggmap)

source("Rtrava.R")

load("token.RData");
# reload the important functions
source("Rtrava.R")
usage_left <- as.integer(c(600, 30000))

Read my activities

my.strava.id<-"845403"
my.acts<-get_activity_list(stoken,id=my.strava.id)

Show a single polyline

first.polyline<-DecodeLineR(my.acts[[1]]$map$summary_polyline)
ggplot(first.polyline,aes(y=lat,x=lng))+
  geom_jitter()+
  geom_path()+
  labs(y="Latitude",x="Longitude")+
  theme_bw(20)

pl.data<-ldply(my.acts,function(cur.act) {
  act.cols<-names(cur.act)
  wt<-cur.act$workout_type
  sum.data<-data.frame(id=cur.act$id
                       )
  tryCatch(
    {
    map.df<-DecodeLineR(cur.act$map$summary_polyline)
    cbind(sum.data,map.df)
    },
    error = function(e) {
      cbind(sum.data,lat=0,lng=0)
    })
})
ggplot(pl.data,aes(x=lng,y=lat))+
  geom_density2d()+
  coord_equal()+
  labs(y="Latitude",x="Longitude")+
  theme_bw(20)

Now show a basic density plot on top of some map information for around Switzerland

villigenMap<-get_map(location=c(lon=8.22190,lat=47.53733),color="bw")
## Map from URL : http://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/staticmap?center=47.53733,8.2219&zoom=10&size=%20640x640&scale=%202&maptype=terrain&sensor=false
## Google Maps API Terms of Service : http://developers.google.com/maps/terms
ggmap(villigenMap)+
  stat_binhex(data=pl.data,aes(x=lng,y=lat),alpha=0.5,bins=200)+
  scale_fill_gradientn(colours=rainbow(6),trans = "log")+
  labs(y="Latitude",x="Longitude")+
  theme_bw(20)
## Warning: Removed 44915 rows containing missing values (stat_hexbin).
